ogg\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9996150907286937, \"rank\": 0.0003849684313289647, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a surprising twist, the iconic rapper and media personality, Snoop Dogg, is set to join NBC's coverage of the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9996150907286937, \"rank\": 0.0003849684313289647, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.317923018984339e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The network revealed that the 52-year-old multi-talented artist will be a Special Correspondent for the Olympic Primetime Show, offering his unique take on the events.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ: Hannah Waddingham passionately defends Tom Cruise criticism  Scheduled to kick off on 26 July 2024, the Paris Olympics will witness Snoop Dogg on the ground, reporting directly from the heart of the action.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Waddingham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hannah Waddingham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Waddingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Waddingham\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC promises viewers a one-of-a-kind experience as Snoop explores Parisian landmarks, attends competitions, and interacts with athletes, their families, and friends as reported byPeople.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9996150907286937, \"rank\": 0.0003849684313289647, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ: Rosario Dawson, 44, excited as she preps for grandmotherhood  Known for his laid-back charm and infectious enthusiasm, Snoop is expected to inject his signature \\\"Snoop style\\\" into the coverage.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosario_Dawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rosario Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosario_Dawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosario_Dawson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will make these games truly unforgettable.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A veteran Olympics enthusiast, Snoop expressed his excitement, saying, \\\"I grew up watching the Olympics, and am thrilled to see the incredible athletes bring their A-game to Paris.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1554, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.317923018984339e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ: Jodie Turner-Smith strolls with friend amidst ex's new romance  It's a celebration of skill, dedication, and the pursuit of greatness.\\\"\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a promise to elevate, celebrate, and make the games unforgettable.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He concluded by saying, \\\"Let us smoke the competition and may the best shine like gold.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peace and Olympic LOVE, ya dig?\\\"\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will not be Snoop's first rodeo with Olympics coverage.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He previously teamed up with Kevin Hart for a highlight show during the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Hart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0891608910384716e-44, \"text\": \"Kevin Hart\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Hart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Hart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ: Florence Pugh takes a hit: Dodging objects at CCXP  Molly Solomon, NBC Olympic Production president and executive producer, credited Snoop's performance during the Tokyo Olympics for earning him the role of Special Correspondent in Paris.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence_Pugh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Florence Pugh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence_Pugh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence_Pugh\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Con_Experience\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CCXP\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Con_Experience\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Con_Experience\"}, {\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"score\": 0.9999997282321061, \"rank\": 2.675380625814223e-07, \"text\": \"Molly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\"}, {\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.317923018984339e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Molly stated, \\\"We do not know what the heck is going to happen every day, but we know he will add his unique perspective to our re-imagined Olympic primetime show.\\\"\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ: Royal decree: King Charles' extravagant demands unveiled!\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement, made during NBC's Sunday Night Football game, revealed that Snoop ha